/* 极简终端风格 — 大厅主界面纯灰度，游戏内容可用彩色 */
/* 原则：全透明背景，继承终端本身的背景色 */

App {
    background: ansi_default;
    color: ansi_default;
}

* {
    scrollbar-size: 1 1;
    scrollbar-background: transparent;
    scrollbar-background-hover: transparent;
    scrollbar-background-active: transparent;
    scrollbar-color: $color-border;
    scrollbar-color-hover: $color-border-light;
    scrollbar-color-active: $color-border-light;
    background: transparent;
}

Static, Horizontal, Vertical {
    background: transparent;
}

Screen {
    layout: vertical;
    background: ansi_default;
    layers: default overlay;
    align: center middle;
}

/* ── 画布 ── */
#canvas {
    height: 1fr;
}

/* ── 拆分容器 ── */
.split-h {
    layout: horizontal;
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
}

.split-v {
    layout: vertical;
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
}

/* ── 窗格包装器（无 width，由 inline fr 权重控制） ── */
.pane-wrapper {
    border: round $color-border;
    height: 1fr;
    min-width: 16;
    min-height: 4;
    background: transparent;
    border-title-background: transparent;
    border-subtitle-background: transparent;
}

.pane-wrapper.--focused {
    border: round $color-fg-secondary;
}

/* ── 空窗格提示 ── */
EmptyPane {
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
    content-align: center middle;
    background: transparent;
}

.empty-hint {
    text-align: center;
    color: $color-fg-tertiary;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    content-align: center middle;
    background: transparent;
}

/* ── RichLog ── */
RichLog {
    background: transparent;
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

RichLog:focus {
    background-tint: transparent;
}

/* ── 面板组件 ── */
ChatPanel, CommandPanel, StatusPanel, OnlineUsersPanel, LoginPanel, AIChatPanel {
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
    background: transparent;
}

AIChatPanel {
    layout: vertical;
}

/* ── 登录面板 ── */
#login-log {
    height: 1fr;
    width: 1fr;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── 面板内输入提示行 ── */
.panel-prompt {
    height: auto;
    max-height: 4;
    display: none;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
}

.panel-prompt.visible {
    display: block;
}

/* ── InputTextArea 基础样式 ── */
InputTextArea {
    height: auto;
    max-height: 4;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0;
    color: $color-fg-primary;
}

InputTextArea:focus {
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
}

/* ── AI 面板常驻顶栏（Tab + 状态） ── */
#ai-chat-header {
    height: auto;
    dock: top;
    display: none;
    background: transparent;
    border: round $color-border;
    padding: 0 1;
}

/* ── AI 聊天日志 ── */
#ai-chat-log {
    scrollbar-size: 1 1;
}

/* ── AI 面板内容区（可滚动） ── */
#ai-panel-content {
    height: 1fr;
    overflow-y: auto;
    scrollbar-size: 1 1;
}

/* ── 物品栏内容（可滚动） ── */
#inventory-content {
    height: 1fr;
    overflow-y: auto;
}

/* ── 指令提示栏 / 聊天输入栏（InputBar 系列） ── */
#cmd-hint-bar, #chat-input-bar, #inventory-input-bar, #ai-input-bar {
    height: auto;
    border: round $color-accent;
    border-title-color: $color-accent;
    padding: 0 1;
    display: none;
}

#cmd-hint-bar.visible, #chat-input-bar.visible, #inventory-input-bar.visible, #ai-input-bar.visible {
    display: block;
}

#cmd-hint-bar {
    max-height: 12;
}

#chat-input-bar {
    max-height: 7;
}

#inventory-input-bar {
    max-height: 7;
}

#ai-input-bar {
    max-height: 8;
}

.input-bar-prompt {
    height: auto;
    max-height: 4;
    width: 100%;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
}

.hint-tabs {
    height: 1;
    width: 100%;
}

.hint-content {
    height: 4;
    width: 100%;
    color: $color-fg-secondary;
    padding: 0 1 0 0;
}

/* ── 底部状态栏 ── */
#footer-bar {
    dock: bottom;
    height: 1;
    background: transparent;
}

#mode-indicator {
    width: 12;
    text-style: bold;
    color: $color-fg-primary;
    content-align: left middle;
    background: transparent;
}

#location-indicator {
    width: auto;
    padding: 0 1;
    background: transparent;
}

#connection-status {
    dock: right;
    width: auto;
    padding: 0 1;
    background: transparent;
}

/* ── which-key 浮动弹窗 ── */
#which-key-overlay {
    layer: overlay;
    display: none;
    width: 80%;
    min-width: 30;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 20;
    border: round $color-accent;
    border-title-color: $color-accent;
    padding: 0 1;
    background: transparent;
}

#which-key-overlay.visible {
    display: block;
}

#wk-tabs {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1;
}

#wk-content {
    width: 100%;
    height: 4;
    color: $color-fg-secondary;
    padding: 0 1 0 0;
}
